txt.en: Kindred to the Dúnedain of Cardolan
You have proven yourself invaluable to the Dúnedain of Cardolan. For this, the Dúnedain of Cardolan now count you among their own.
You must earn Kindred standing with the Dúnedain of Cardolan
The Dúnedain of Cardolan count you among their own, and your deeds will be remembered for ages to come.
